ets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"建制27個，泛民17個，點都唔夠票"},{"pid":"96cd10c7b148722942b381843789e99cf2439778","tid":2264383,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"郭家麒：議會現在稍為回復正常<br />\n<br />\n邊忽度正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------<br />\n2020年10月23日<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會資訊科技及廣播事務委員會第二次會議仍未選出正副主席。<br />\n<br />\n正副主席的選舉由上一立法年度主席莫乃光主持，民主派議員提名多人角逐，建制派只有何君堯一名候選人。<br />\n<br />\n莫乃光提議每名候選人投票前有兩分鐘發表政綱，設有質詢環節及候選人回應時間。建制派不同意有關安排，認為是浪費會議時間。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯：「按你的編排表面是公平，實際上不公正。如果下個會議未能選出主席，我會敦請大主席將你身分及資格革除，簡單講是『DQ你』。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">郭家麒：「有沒有搞錯？議會現在稍為回復正常，所有委員會不容討論政綱，<span class=\"x-large\">全部好像人大拍手通過，你是否想議會淪落至此才收手？</span>」</span><br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<br />\n乜而家立法會唔係人大咩???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0b0cefd7dc912cae308e7063d4d656b933c43a","tid":2264383,"uid":143499,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4eeb191ee6819f28064c58f15c4ddf7e21cf1e2","tid":2264383,"uid":273703,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:10:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c4798ab2b2110fcd649fed74fbaf4a605d69b27","tid":2264383,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"496f5170facbf0fb3e7d0eeeed635f43b2cd1e0a","tid":2264383,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"56f44e3b5b4163b8532c9181f60b2b6f88b0eb9a","tid":2264383,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VaLtpzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVaLtpzo.jpg&h=b88f92ec&s={SIZE}\" /><